Others: Bafana Bafana play Congo Brazzaville in the Afcon qualifiers on October 11 and 15, 2024.
Hugo Broos' men are currently second in Group K with two matches played.
If Bafana wins both matches against Congo, they will have 10 points and be on the verge of qualifying for the Afcon.
Uganda is also a contender for qualification, and if they win their matches against South Sudan and Bafana wins against Congo, Bafana should qualify alongside Uganda.
Luke le Roux has been called up to the squad after the withdrawal of two players.
Le Roux has urged Bafana fans to come in their number for the Afcon qualifier against Congo Brazzaville.
